OL,3,CMan charged after suspicious device
OL,4,Cprompted evacuation
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court after
OL,7,Fhomes were evacuated following reports
OL,8,Fof a suspicious device in Sheffield.
OL,10,FPolice and bomb disposal experts were
OL,11,Fcalled to Washington Road after the
OL,12,Falarm was raised on Wednesday morning.
OL,14,FA large area was cordoned off for
OL,15,Fseveral hours and residents were told
OL,16,Fto leave their homes.
OL,18,FThe device was later found to be
OL,19,Fharmless, South Yorkshire Police said.
