OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774008171
OL,3,CMan charged after suspicious device
OL,4,Cprompted evacuation
OL,6,FSteven Budzizewski, 56, appeared at
OL,7,FSheffield Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FThursday charged with intentionally or
OL,9,Frecklessly causing a public nuisance
OL,10,Fand affray.
OL,12,FHe was remanded into custody to appear
OL,13,Fat Sheffield Crown Court on 9 April.
OL,15,FSupt Martin Simcock said: "I
OL,16,Fappreciate that yesterday's incident
OL,17,Fwill have caused disruption for some
OL,18,Fresidents, and I would like to thank
OL,19,Fthe local community for their patience
OL,20,Fand cooperation as officers carried
OL,21,Fout necessary checks."
